            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>Lucius Numisius Primus, Lucius Numisius Optatus, Lucius Melissaeus Plocamus, ministers of Fortuna Augusta, by decree of the decurions, issued by Lucius Iulius Ponticus and Publius Gavius Pastor the duumvirs in charge of speaking the law, Quintus Poppaeus and Caius Vibius aediles, when Quintus Futius and Publius Calvisius were consuls. </p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The same Lucius Melissaeus Plocamus can be found in EDCS-70900323/EDR146024. The same C. Vibius, here an aedile, is perhaps to be found in <ref target="EmpWor000223.xml">EmpWor000223</ref>.</p> 
            </div>
